commits.commitMessage:
Add qmi_shutdown_modem

Effect Platform:
AR759x Release 1: Yes
AR759x Release 2: Yes

This commit is for added for QTI9X40-3025.
1, /etc/init.d/modem_shutdown invoke an application "qmi_shutdown_modem".
2, This application is used to do PC mode transition and UIM powerdown task.
3, But it doesn't take effect in sierra code.
4, Enable the "qmi_shutdown_modem" application.
5, Fix the bug system stuck when excute "qmi_shutdown_modem --immediately".
6, More details about point 5 can be found QTI9X28-2655.

Resolves: QTI9X40-3025
Change-Id: Idb535f8fa3b9e5b251514c4e552a82d9781b03a0
Signed-off-by: Felix Zhu <FZhu@sierrawireless.com>
commits.subject: Add qmi_shutdown_modem
